+msgid "Open Embedded Linux Entertainment Center (OpenELEC) is a minimal Linux distribution purpose built for PlexHT media center. OpenELEC is designed to boot fast with an installation process simple enough for anyone to convert a bare HTPC into a fully configured media machine in under 15 minutes."
